result.execSummary:
The defendant Joanie Christine Jones was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Joanie Christine Jones is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Joanie Christine Jones was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Misdemeanor, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
